title: Mac NWN 1.69 Patches (English)
description:
The Final Patch for the original Neverwinter Nights game.

All versions of the patch are included, just download the one you need.


Not sure which one you need?

NWNMac169_English.zip
 If you ONLY have NWN and no expansions installed

XP1Mac169_English.zip
 If you have NWN and SoU installed but NOT HoU

XP2Mac169_English.zip
 If you have NWN,SoU, and HoU installed (Also for 
Platinum/Diamond editions)

Patch details <a href=" http://nwn.bioware.com/support/patchdetails169.html" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://nwn.bioware.com/support/patchdetails169.html</a>

Enjoy!
